{"pageid":324200,"pagename":"Praying to the Gods","title":"Praying to the Gods","displaytitle":"Praying to the Gods","revid":14166940,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Chaos_Fanatic.png"},{"name":"description","value":"Praying to the Gods is a hard combat achievement which requires the player to \"Kill the Chaos Fanatic 10 times without drinking any potion which restores prayer or leaving the Wilderness.\" Logging out does not reset your progress."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-task\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"infobox-header\" colspan=\"5\"><b>Praying to the Gods</b>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-full-width-content\" colspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/w/File:Chaos_Fanatic.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Chaos Fanatic.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Chaos_Fanatic.png/150px-Chaos_Fanatic.png?8871d\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"265\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Chaos_Fanatic.png/225px-Chaos_Fanatic.png?8871d 1.5x, /images/thumb/Chaos_Fanatic.png/300px-Chaos_Fanatic.png?8871d 2x\" data-file-width=\"550\" data-file-height=\"973\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Released\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/21_July\" title=\"21 July\">21 July</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Update:Combat Achievements\">Update</a>)\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Task\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">Kill the Chaos Fanatic 10 times without drinking any potion which restores prayer or leaving the Wilderness.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">Yes\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Area\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">West of the <a href=\"/w/Lava_Maze\" title=\"Lava Maze\">Lava Maze</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Reward\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">None\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Achievement_Diary\" title=\"Achievement Diary\">Diary</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Combat Achievements\">Combat Achievements</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Tier\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Hard\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Hard\">Hard</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><b>Praying to the Gods</b> is a <a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Hard\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Hard\">hard combat achievement</a> which requires the player to \"Kill the <a href=\"/w/Chaos_Fanatic\" title=\"Chaos Fanatic\">Chaos Fanatic</a> 10 times without drinking any potion which restores <a href=\"/w/Prayer\" title=\"Prayer\">prayer</a> or leaving the <a href=\"/w/Wilderness\" title=\"Wilderness\">Wilderness</a>.\" Logging out does not reset your progress.\n</p><p>This task prohibits the consumption of only the following items:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Prayer_potion\" title=\"Prayer potion\">Prayer potion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Zamorak_brew\" title=\"Zamorak brew\">Zamorak brew</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Super_restore\" title=\"Super restore\">Super restore</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Sanfew_serum\" title=\"Sanfew serum\">Sanfew serum</a></li></ul>\n<p>This means it is allowed to make use of several other prayer-restoring items, which notably includes the <a href=\"/w/Falador_shield\" title=\"Falador shield\">Falador shields</a>. <a href=\"/w/Jangerberries\" title=\"Jangerberries\">Jangerberries</a> and yellow <a href=\"/w/Spicy_stew\" title=\"Spicy stew\">spicy stew</a> also do not cause failure of this task, however both of these items are not recommended for practical use. Players can also use the <a href=\"/w/Special_attack\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Special attack\">special attack</a> on the <a href=\"/w/Saradomin_godsword\" title=\"Saradomin godsword\">Saradomin godsword</a> or <a href=\"/w/Ancient_mace\" title=\"Ancient mace\">ancient mace</a> to recharge their prayer, however due to the fanatic's high melee defences this an unreliable way to restore prayer points.\n</p><p>While leaving the <a href=\"/w/Wilderness\" title=\"Wilderness\">Wilderness</a> is not allowed for this achievement, it is allowed to pray at an <a href=\"/w/Altar\" title=\"Altar\">altar</a> and to make use of the <a href=\"/w/Wilderness_Obelisk\" title=\"Wilderness Obelisk\">Wilderness Obelisk</a> network. This means the easiest way to achieve this is to gear up for 10 kills of the <a href=\"/w/Chaos_Fanatic\" title=\"Chaos Fanatic\">Chaos Fanatic</a>, and simply pray at an altar to restore prayer points in between the kills. Players with lower <a href=\"/w/Prayer\" title=\"Prayer\">Prayer</a> levels who cannot complete a full kill without recharging their prayer points halfway through the battle can also run away from the fight, pray at an altar, and then continue their kill. Doing so does not reset progress of this achievement.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Praying_to_the_Gods?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Strategy\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Praying_to_the_Gods?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Strategy\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The suggested strategy for completing this task is to make use of the <a href=\"/w/Wilderness_Obelisk\" title=\"Wilderness Obelisk\">Wilderness Obelisk</a> network, after having completed the <a href=\"/w/Wilderness_Diary#Hard\" title=\"Wilderness Diary\">hard Wilderness Diary</a> which allows players to set a custom destination. Using these obelisks, players can teleport to the level 13 obelisk, then recharge their prayer at the altar just <b>outside</b> the <a href=\"/w/Ferox_Enclave\" title=\"Ferox Enclave\">Ferox Enclave</a>, and then return to the level 44 obelisk to continue on the task. Note that entering the Enclave does reset progress, so the altar just east of it needs to be used.\n</p><p>Players who have not completed the hard Wilderness Diary may opt instead to use the <a href=\"/w/Chaos_Altar_(Prayer)\" title=\"Chaos Altar (Prayer)\">Chaos Altar</a> found in the <a href=\"/w/Chaos_Temple_(hut)\" title=\"Chaos Temple (hut)\">deep Wilderness Chaos Temple</a>, which is just south-west of the Chaos Fanatic. However, due to this location being commonly patrolled by <a href=\"/w/Player_killing\" title=\"Player killing\">PKers</a> and being a <a href=\"/w/Multicombat_area\" title=\"Multicombat area\">multicombat area</a>, it is recommended to take more caution when using this altar.\n</p>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Combat Achievements\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Template:Combat Achievements\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Combat_Achievements\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Combat_Achievements?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a hr